<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>AmicBridge – Structured Lending, Borrowing & Investing</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <meta name="description" content="AmicBridge is a private network where people lend, borrow, and invest with written agreements, clear expectations, and shared profit. Trust before money." />

  <!-- Open Graph -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="AmicBridge – Structured Lending, Borrowing & Investing" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="Private lending and investing network built on trust, agreements and fairness." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://amicbridge.com" />

  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #2563eb;
      --background: #ffffff;
      --text: #0f172a;
      --muted: #475569;
      --border: #e2e8f0;
      --card: #ffffff;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif;
      color: var(--text);
      background: var(--background);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    header {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 16px 20px;
    }

    .brand-block {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    }

    .logo span {
      color: var(--primary);
    }

    .top-meta {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    nav {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    nav a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
      font-size: 14px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    nav a:hover {
      background: #f1f5f9;
    }

    nav a:focus-visible,
    a:focus-visible,
    button:focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid var(--primary);
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1024px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 24px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .trust-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      background: #f1f5f9;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 34px;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn-primary,
    .btn-secondary {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 9px 16px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 14px;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--text);
      background: #f8fafc;
    }

    .hero-card {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 14px;
      background: var(--card);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }

    .hero-card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero-pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
    }

    .hero-pill {
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #f1f5f9;
    }

    section {
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .contact-card {
      margin-top: 10px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 12px;
      background: var(--card);
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
    }

    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 16px 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
<header>
  <div class="brand-block">
    <div class="logo">AMIC<span>BRIDGE</span></div>
    <div class="top-meta">Based in Norway · Private lending & investing network</div>
  </div>

  <nav aria-label="Main navigation">
    <a href="#how">How it works</a>
    <a href="#who">Who it is for</a>
    <a href="#trust">Trust & agreements</a>
    <a href="#currency">Currency</a>
    <a href="#stablecoin">Stablecoin</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<main class="container">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div>
      <div class="trust-tag"><span>✔</span> TRUST BEFORE MONEY</div>

      <h1>Structured lending, borrowing and investing between people.</h1>

      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        AmicBridge is a private network where people help each other with capital –
        always with written agreements, clear expectations and realistic profit sharing.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Contact CEO</a>
        <a href="#how" class="btn-secondary">Learn how it works</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <aside class="hero-card" aria-label="AmicBridge summary">
      <h3>AmicBridge in one look</h3>
      <div class="hero-pill-row">
        <span class="hero-pill">Written agreements</span>
        <span class="hero-pill">Clear expectations</span>
        <span class="hero-pill">No hidden fees</span>
        <span class="hero-pill">Human-to-human network</span>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT SECTIONS -->
  <section id="how">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <p>
      People can lend, borrow or invest inside a private trusted network.
      Everything is voluntary, transparent and documented.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="who">
    <h2>Who it is for</h2>
    <p>
      It is for responsible people who respect agreements,
      value trust, and believe financial relationships should benefit both sides.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="trust">
    <h2>Trust & Written Agreements</h2>
    <p>
      Every financial action has a written agreement with clear terms:
      repayment expectations, risks, responsibilities and benefits.
      Trust first. Money second.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="currency">
    <h2>Currency</h2>
    <p>
      Operations can be recorded and executed in relevant currencies and stable
      value units depending on region, regulation and practicality.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="stablecoin">
    <h2>Stablecoin Direction</h2>
    <p>
      Long term vision includes stable, transparent digital value units backed by trust
      and real agreements — not speculation.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Interested in being part of AmicBridge?</p>

    <div class="contact-card">
      <strong>CEO:</strong>  
      <div>Name: Your Name</div>
      <div>Email: your@email.com</div>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<footer>
  <span>© <span id="year"></span> AmicBridge · Trust Before Money</span>
  <span>Private financial network.</span>
</footer>

<script>
  document.getElementById('year').textContent = new Date().getFullYear();
</script>

</body>
</html>
